              <li>Support various multimedia formats for a diverse range of content (videos, podcasts, images).</li>
              <li>Ensure compatibility with popular streaming services.</li>
            </ul>
          </li>

          <li>
            <p><strong>Social Media Integration:</strong></p>
            <ul>
              <li>Integrate social media sharing buttons and feeds.</li>
              <li>Allow users to log in using social media accounts.</li>
            </ul>
          </li>

          <li>
            <p><strong>Analytics and Monitoring:</strong></p>
