              <li>Implement secure payment gateways for any e-commerce or subscription services.</li>
              <li>Comply with industry standards for online transactions.</li>
            </ul>
          </li>

          <li>
            <p><strong>Accessibility:</strong></p>
            <ul>
              <li>Adhere to accessibility standards (WCAG) to make the website inclusive for users with disabilities.</li>
              <li>Provide alternative text for images and ensure keyboard navigation.</li>
            </ul>
          </li>

          <li>
            <p><strong>Backup and Recovery:</strong></p>
            <ul>
              <li>Regularly backup website data and implement a robust recovery plan.</li>
